Package: marpoly
Type: Package
Title: Mixed Causal-Noncausal Autoregressions and Polyspectral Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel", "Velasquez-Gaviria", email = "d.velasquezgaviria@maastrichtuniversity.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Alain", "Hecq", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Tools for mixed causal-noncausal autoregressive models and higher-order polyspectral analysis. The package implements simulation of MAR(r,s) processes, second-, third-, and fourth-order periodograms and spectral densities, frequency-domain minimum-distance estimation, all root allocations for a selected autoregressive order, residual extraction, and diagnostic plotting.
